reviewText:
This is a typical teasing from Peach Girls.  Sole dancer is to undress all her mini clothing.  Her aim is not to show off her curve.
Photo shot is to reveal her shaven private part.  Done.  Next.  Girl after Girl...  This adult entertainment may be justified to
club goers and business deals.  Invitation but no real thing.
Speaking of the dancers, everyone of them looks about 40 something.  Lights are bright enough.

This is one of the best  Peach releases out there, although much if not all of it is rehashed material from other  releases.  The good of course is that it's  a kind of "greatest hits."

Actually, I could replace that last "h" with a "t," because these are some of the most beautiful breasts that Peach ever has featured,  and almost all are wonderfully natural. Jesse Capelli, Kira Eggers, Jamie Lynn, Ginger Jolie...the list  goes on. And  this also  is  explicit enough to keep your attention.

It's pretty typical for Peach in presentation: Run time roughly an hour,  multiple vignettes with different women, each vignette goes about five minutes. And there is a behind-the scene feature that goes about eight minutes (interviews with several of the models) and the requisite package of four trailers.

Overall a good buy.

I've had these DVDs for some time.  I found them on Amazon but wonder if they are still available.
They feature lovely, seductive girls well versed in the art of striptease.  If you like this sort of thing,
you'll find it all in good taste and very entertaining; ladies too.
